     │
     ▼
  Render (Backend)
  Spring Boot REST API
  Business Layer
  DAO / Data Layer
     │
     ▼
  Clever Cloud
  PostgreSQL Database

📁 Project Structure
  plant-tracker
  ├── client/                     # React + Vite frontend
  │   ├── public
  │   └── src
  │       ├── assets
  │       └── components
  │
